The '''K'rom wars''' were a series of conflicts involving the [[Xi'Dec/Legends|Xi'Dec]] people. During these wars, several new [[Gender/Legends|sexes]] of Xi'Dec arose which were specialized for combat. These Xi'Dec had specialized forelimbs used as spears or sabers.

